style meat lasag
Cooking Instructions
Ingredients: Pasta (Durum Wheat Semolina
[Enriched With Niacin, Iron, Thiamin Mononitrate,
Riboflavin, Folic Acid], Water, Powdered Egg
White), Water, Ricotta Cheese (Whey, Milk,
Bacterial Culture, Salt, Citric Acid), Beef, Pork, Low
Moisture Partly Skimmed Mozzarella Cheese (Partly
Skimmed Milk, Bacterial Culture, Salt, Calcium
Chloride, Microbial Enzymes), Crushed Tomatoes,
Diced Tomatoes (Tomatoes, Tomato Juice, Citric
Acid, Calcium Chloride), Onions, Vinegar, Modified
Cornstarch, Skim Milk Powder, Romano Cheese
(Milk, Bacterial Culture, Calcium Chloride, Lipase,
Rennet, Salt), Salt, Flavor Base (Salt, Autolysed
Yeast Extract, Sugar, Maltodextrin, Soya Protein
Concentrate, Onion Powder, Caramel, Carrot
Powder, Garlic Powder, Spices, Flavor, Beef, Beef
Fat, Beef Stock, Soya Lecithin, Xanthan Gum),
Garlic, Sugar, Parmesan Cheese (Milk, Salt, Lipase,
Calcium Chloride, Microbial Enzyme, Bacterial
Culture), Spices, Autolysed Yeast Extract, Crushed
Red Chili Peppers, Dried Parsley.
For best results, prepare in conventional oven.
Conventional Oven:
1. Pre-heat oven to 375°F
2. Reove tray from box and pull back
two čorners of the film slightly to vent.
3. Place container on baking sheet and
place in oven on center rack.
4. Cook for 60-70 min. Carefully remove
film entirely and cook for an additional
10 min. to brown cheese.
Co
tr.
an
5. Carefully remove from oven. Allow to
stand for 5 min. before serving.

these
Microwave Oven: (Best of luck!)
1. Remove tray from box. Pierce film with
only. C
tempe
fork to vent.
2. Place tray in microwave and cook on
high power for 6 min.
3. Let tray rest in microwave for 3-4 min.
4. Cook on high power for 6 min.
5. Let tray rest in microwave for 3-4 min.
6. Cook on high power for 3-4 min.
7. Carefully remove tray from microwave.
Remove plastic film.
Contains Wheat, Egg, Milk & Soy.
Dist & Sold Exclusively By:
Trader Joe's, Monrovia, Ca 91016
8. Let tray stand for 3 min. before serving.
